text: If everybody keeps misusing ridesharing" to mean ride-hailing, that problem isn't going away"
Yeah ride-hailing. We use raidesharing as most end users are not familiar with ride-hailing
Could you clarify? You keep using the term ride-sharing but you mean ride-hailing, right? Different things.
